name: FAITH IN HELL
description:
Faith came to visit me, and we decided to take a walk with her.
I haven't seen her for a long time, I miss her.

We went for a walk through the expanses of hell, 
admired all sorts of sins, talked a lot ..

In the course of the dialogue, we came to the conclusion 
that hell is a special reward that is received by those who persistently desired it.
...
At the end of the day, we had sex so powerfully with Faith 
that the Hell's Church burned to the ground.

Together with Faith.
